document_data.Into The Silver Realm:
{{Main|Dungeon magazine 43/Into The Silver Realm}}
: ''By [[Steve Kurtz]], illustrated by [[David O. Miller]], Cartography by [[Diesel]].'' '''p. 52-72'''
Never, ever steal a silver sword. A 20 page adventure situated near [[Mirabar]] and in the [[Astral Plane]] intended for 4-8 neutral and good player characters of 8th-12th level (about 60 total levels). The DM will need access to ''[[The Complete Psionics Handbook]]''. {{Dusup|43/Into The Silver Realm}}
